span><span class="text-lg font-semibold tracking-wide text-gray-300">Uber</span><span class="text-lg font-semibold tracking-wide text-gray-300">Microsoft</span><span class="text-lg font-semibold tracking-wide text-gray-300">ElevenLabs</span><span class="text-lg font-semibold tracking-wide text-gray-300">HubSpot</span></div></section><section id="how-it-works" class="relative z-10 py-24"><div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><h2 class="mb-4 text-center text-3xl font-bold sm:text-4xl">How you Do it with Doable</h2><div class="mt-16 grid gap-12 md:grid-cols-3"><div class="text-center"><div class="mx-auto mb-4 flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-gray-800"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-lightbulb h-7 w-7 text-brand-400"><path d="M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-.9 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.7 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5"></path><path d="M9 18h6"></path><path d="M10 22h4"></path></svg></div><h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold">Say what you want to do</h3><p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-400">Describe your app, drop in screenshots, or share docs. Doable gets it.</p></div><div class="text-center"><div class="mx-auto mb-4 flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-gray-800"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-wand-sparkles h-7 w-7 text-brand-400"><path d="m21.64 3.64-1.28-1.28a1.21 1.21 0 0 0-1.72 0L2.36 18.64a1.21 1.21 0 0 0 0 1.72l1.28 1.28a1.2 1.2 0 0 0 1.72 0L21.64 5.36a1.2 1.2 0 0 0 0-1.72"></path><path d="m14 7 3 3"></path><path d="M5 6v4"></path><path d="M19 14v4"></path><path d="M10 2v2"></path><path d="M7 8H3"></path><path d="M21 16h-4"></path><path d="M11 3H9"></path></svg></div><h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold">Watch Doable doing it</h3><p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-400">AI writes the code, builds the UI, and sets up the backend while you watch.</p></div><div class="text-center"><div class="mx-auto mb-4 flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-gray-800"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-send h-7 w-7 text-brand-400"><path d="M14.536 21.686a.5.5 0 0 0 .937-.024l6.5-19a.496.496 0 0 0-.635-.635l-19 6.5a.5.5 0 0 0-.024.937l7.93 3.18a2 2 0 0 1 1.112 1.11z"></path><path d="m21.854 2.147-10.94 10.939"></path></svg></div><h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold">Done. Ship it.</h3><p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-400">One click deploy. Custom domains, SSL, and global CDN all done for you.</p></div></div></div></section><section id="features" class="relative z-10 border-t border-gray-800/50 py-24"><div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><h2 class="mb-4 text-center text-3xl font-bold sm:text-4xl">Everything you need to get it done</h2><p class="mx-auto mb-16 max-w-xl text-center text-gray-400">All the tools built in so you keep doing, not configuring. Doable handles the rest.</p><div class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4"><div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-800 bg-[#111] p-6 transition-colors hover:border-gray-700"><div class="mb-3 inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-gray-800"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-gauge h-5 w-5 text-brand-400"><path d="m12 14 4-4"></path><path d="M3.34 19a10 10 0 1 1 17.32 0"></path></svg></div><h3 class="mb-1 font-semibold">Lightning fast</h3><p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-400">Optimized builds and edge deployment for sub-second load times.</p></div><div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-800 bg-[#111] p-6 transition-colors hover:border-gray-700"><div class="mb-3 inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-gray-800"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-lock h-5 w-5 text-brand-400"><rect width="18" height="11" x="3" y="11" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"></path></svg></div><h3 class="mb-1 font-semibold">Secure by default</h3><p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-400">Enterprise-grade security with automatic SSL and DDoS protection.</p></div><div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-800 bg-[#111] p-6 transition-colors hover:border-gray-700"><div class="mb-3 inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-gray-800"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-earth h-5 w-5 text-brand-400"><path d="M21.54 15H17a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v4.54"></path><path d="M7 3.34V5a3 3 0 0 0 3 3a2 2 0 0 1 2 2c0 1.1.9 2 2 2a2 2 0 0 0 2-2c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h3.17"></path><path d="M11 21.95V18a2 2 0 0 0-2-2a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-1a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H2.05"></path><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></div><h3 class="mb-1 font-semibold">Global CDN</h3><p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-400">Your app served from 200+ edge locations worldwide.</p></div><div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-800 bg-[#111] p-6 transition-colors hover:border-gray-700"><div class="mb-3 inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-gray-800"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-braces h-5 w-5 text-brand-400"><path d="M8 3H7a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v5a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 2 2 0 0 1 2 2v5c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h1"></path><path d="M16 21h1a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-5c0-1.1.9-2 2-2a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-1"></path></svg></div><h3 class="mb-1 font-semibold">Full code access</h3><p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-400">Export your code anytime. No lock-in, ever.</p></div></div></div></section><section id="pricing" class="relative z-10 py-24"><div class="relative mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 text-center"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0"><div class="absolute left-1/2 top-1/2 h-[300px] w-[500px] -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 rounded-full bg-brand-600/10 blur-[100px]"></div></div><div class="relative"><h2 class="mb-4 text-3xl font-bold sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl">Ready to do this? Doable is.</h2><p class="mx-auto mb-8 max-w-xl text-gray-400">Thousands of makers are already doing it with Doable. Start for free. No credit card required.</p><div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3 sm:flex-row"><a class="inline-flex items-center justify-center whitespace-nowrap ring-offset-background transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 py-2 h-12 rounded-full bg-white px-8 text-sm font-semibold text-black hover:bg-gray-200" href="/signup">Start doing for free</a><a class="inline-flex items-center justify-center whitespace-nowrap font-medium ring-offset-background transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 hover:bg-accent py-2 h-12 rounded-full px-8 text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-white" href="#how-it-works">Learn more</a></div><p class="mt-4 text-xs text-gray-600">Free forever for personal projects. Just do it with Doable.</p></div></div></sectio